      "baseline": 18
    },
    {
      "id": "txt-161",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 40,
      "y": 1095,
      "width": 450.45000000000005,
      "height": 81.25,
      "angle": 0,
      "strokeColor": "#1E2D40",
      "backgroundColor": "transparent",
      "fillStyle": "solid",
      "strokeWidth": 2,
      "strokeStyle": "solid",
      "roughness": 1,
      "opacity": 100,
      "seed": 161,
      "version": 1,
      "versionNonce": 162,
      "isDeleted": false,
      "groupIds": [],
      "frameId": null,
      "roundness": null,
      "boundElements": [],
      "updated": 1779366151593,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "fontSize": 13,
      "fontFamily": 2,
      "text": "Sprint 1 — Quick wins (1 semana):\n  • Conectar Prisma Accelerate (1 línea en DATABASE_URL).\n  • Habilitar Upstash Redis en prod + middleware de rate-limit.\n  • Migrar emails a Resend (mantener Gmail como fallback).\n  • Activar Vercel BotID en /api/v1/auth/*.",
      "originalText": "Sprint 1 — Quick wins (1 semana):\n  • Conectar Prisma Accelerate (1 línea en DATABASE_URL).\n  • Habilitar Upstash Redis en prod + middleware de rate-limit.\n  • Migrar emails a Resend (mantener Gmail como fallback).\n  • Activar Vercel BotID en /api/v1/auth/*.",
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "lineHeight": 1.25,
      "baseline": 12
    },
    {
      "id": "txt-163",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 820,
      "y": 1095,
      "width": 436.15000000000003,
      "height": 81.25,
      "angle": 0,
      "strokeColor": "#1E2D40",
      "backgroundColor": "transparent",
      "fillStyle": "solid",
      "strokeWidth": 2,
      "strokeStyle": "solid",
      "roughness": 1,
      "opacity": 100,
      "seed": 163,
      "version": 1,
      "versionNonce": 164,
      "isDeleted": false,
      "groupIds": [],
      "frameId": null,
      "roundness": null,
      "boundElements": [],
      "updated": 1779366151593,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "fontSize": 13,
      "fontFamily": 2,
      "text": "Sprint 2 — Resiliencia (2 semanas):\n  • Mover webhooks (Stripe/Breezeway/Guesty) a Vercel Queues.\n  • Audit logs vía queue (no bloquean el response).\n  • Cache de BigQuery por (filtros, día) con TTL 15min.\n  • Cloud SQL → Private IP + VPC Connector.",
      "originalText": "Sprint 2 — Resiliencia (2 semanas):\n  • Mover webhooks (Stripe/Breezeway/Guesty) a Vercel Queues.\n  • Audit logs vía queue (no bloquean el response).\n  • Cache de BigQuery por (filtros, día) con TTL 15min.\n  • Cloud SQL → Private IP + VPC Connector.",
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "lineHeight": 1.25,
      "baseline": 12
    },
    {
      "id": "txt-165",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 1600,
      "y": 1095,
      "width": 350.35,
      "height": 81.25,
      "angle": 0,
      "strokeColor": "#1E2D40",
      "backgroundColor": "transparent",
      "fillStyle": "solid",
      "strokeWidth": 2,
      "strokeStyle": "solid",
      "roughness": 1,
      "opacity": 100,
      "seed": 165,
      "version": 1,
      "versionNonce": 166,
      "isDeleted": false,
      "groupIds": [],
      "frameId": null,
      "roundness": null,
      "boundElements": [],
      "updated": 1779366151593,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "fontSize": 13,
      "fontFamily": 2,
      "text": "Sprint 3 — Observability (1 semana):\n  • Sentry DSN poblado + source maps.\n  • Vercel Analytics + Speed Insights.\n  • Alert en Slack si p95 > 2s o error rate > 1%.\n  • Dashboard de cuotas (DB, BQ, emails).",
      "originalText": "Sprint 3 — Observability (1 semana):\n  • Sentry DSN poblado + source maps.\n  • Vercel Analytics + Speed Insights.\n  • Alert en Slack si p95 > 2s o error rate > 1%.\n  • Dashboard de cuotas (DB, BQ, emails).",
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "lineHeight": 1.25,
      "baseline": 12
    }
